<paragraph id="IFRS15_B82" base="F31717100"><paranum>B82</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 15"/><data name="paranum" value="B82"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS15_P0795">If an entity recognises <xref base="F31716759" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_P0508">revenue<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0341"/></ph></xref> for the sale of a product on a bill-and-hold basis, the entity shall consider whether it has remaining <xref base="F31716748" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_P0504">performance obligations<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0288"/></ph></xref> (for example, for custodial services) in accordance with <xref id="IFRS15_X0796" base="F33214804" href="IFRS15_22.dita#IFRS15_22">paragraphs 22&#x2013;30</xref> to which the entity shall allocate a portion of the <xref base="F31716779" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_P0510">transaction price<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0370"/></ph></xref> in accordance with <xref id="IFRS15_X0797" base="F33214805" href="IFRS15_73.dita#IFRS15_73">paragraphs 73&#x2013;86</xref>.</p></body></paragraph>